# Gmail
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User akisarou90@gmail.com
PassCmd "oama access akisarou90@gmail.com"
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Sync All


